00:19:24,500 --> 00:19:26,900
Sir, the XO can barely stand.

259
00:19:28,100 --> 00:19:29,380
He's got a rash, and the med--

260
00:19:29,420 --> 00:19:33,380
Chief, we're in hostile waters, the XO
